Paul

Handle some FS exceptions more elegantly (#4202)

If Documents/Surge was very misconfigured fs couldn't recurse
it and threw an exception which we left uncaught. That crashed
surge. So catch it and handle the error instead in the few startup
path spots.

Closes #4200